data.title: Resistance @ Privilege Ibiza — TPi
data.meta_description: Ultra Enterprises has spent its 2nd consecutive summer in Ibiza, delivering 9-weeks of Resistance at the world’s largest nightclub. In keeping with the group’s consistent production values, a special Funktion-One Vero sound system was deployed for each event, along with an exquisite show design and a talented tech team. TPi hit the White Isle to […]
